init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I'm sorry Mr. President, but this is no joke.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: John F. Kennedy, and I'm calling you from the year 2035.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I know it's hard to believe, but I'm really here.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You're telling me that in 2025, aliens are going to attack us?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Because the world will not believe us.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: they were a group of humans who were working with the Xeno-Sapiens.
